## Quick Fix: If You Don't Want to Migrate

Just add some sample data manually via Admin Panel or API:

```bash
# Add a sample movie via curl
curl -X POST https://chalchitra-api.onrender.com/api/movies/add \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"title":"Sample Movie","description":"Test","price":200,"venue":"Hall 1"}'
```

