## Summary

| Task | Action |
|------|--------|
| Export local data | `sqlite3 database.db ".dump movies" > movies.sql` |
| Create Render DB | Render Dashboard → New PostgreSQL |
| Add connection string | Render Web Service → Environment → DATABASE_URL |
| Create tables | Run `init-db.js` on Render |
| Import data | Run `migrate-to-render.js` |
| Restart | Trigger new deploy on Render |

